comments: You learn to like him very much, he is a down to earth person, and a very good professor, we need more of his kind here in The United States.

This guy was great. The lecture was easy to understand. He has a study guide that was cheap and there was no need for a text book (i didn\'t read it once waste of money). His tests are easy if you study his study guide and he\'s nice. He does take roll and doesn\'t let class out early =(
HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!! THIS PROFESSOR IS VERY ENLIGHTENING!!! AWESOME! NO WORDS CAN DESCRIBE, TAKE THIS CLASS!!!
